# 1. PURPOSE

Defines policy rules for government core structures.

# 2. POLICY RULES

- government scope must be explicit
- governing authority and active term must be explicit
- overlapping incompatible active terms are prohibited
- ambiguous governing authority is prohibited

# 3. FAILURE RULE

- missing government scope must reject
- incompatible active term overlap must reject
- ambiguous governing authority must reject

